MAT|20|5||and they went. And again he went out at the sixth and ninth hours, and did the same.
MAT|20|6||And about the eleventh hour, he went out and found others who were standing and idle; and he said to them: Why stand ye all the day, and are idle?
MAT|20|7||They say to him, Because no one hath hired us. He saith to them: Go ye also into the vineyard; and what is right ye shall receive.
