ACT|13|30||But God raised him from the dead.
ACT|13|31||And he was seen many days, by them who came up with him from Galilee to Jerusalem; and they are now his witnesses to the people.
ACT|13|32||And lo, we also announce to you, that the promise, which was made to our fathers,
